                <div class="mt-xxl-3"><p class="sub d-inline">An agentic pipeline that turns a prompt into analytical dashboards. </p><p class="sub d-none d-xxl-inline">Built for your team's daily data visualisation tasks with highest performance and lowest cost.</p></div>
