      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="num">02</div>
        <h3>Bilboard plans and builds</h3>
        <p>Agents choose the right components, plan the layout, and assemble a coherent dashboard skeleton behind the scenes.</p>
        <svg class="step-arrow" width="24" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 14" fill="none"><path d="M0 7h22M16 1l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="num">03</div>
        <h3>Export or keep iterating</h3>
