      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q"><span>Who is it for?</span><span class="plus"></span></button>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>Blazor developers, internal-tools teams, and AI builders who need to ship dashboards quickly without rewriting boilerplate every time.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q"><span>Can I customize the generated dashboard?</span><span class="plus"></span></button>
        <div class="faq-a"><p>Absolutely. Output is clean Razor markup — edit it directly, iterate with follow-up prompts, or extend it with your own BIL components.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

